		"description": "<div class=\"page\" title=\"Page 39\">\n<div class=\"layoutArea\">\n<div class=\"column\">\n<p>With an explosive pop on impact your attack releases noxious smoke. Make a ranged attack as normal. If this attack hits your target, it bursts into a cloud of gas with a 15ft cube centered on your target&rsquo;s square until the end of your next turn. Each creature that starts their turn in or moves through the smoke must make a constitution save against your maneuver DC or have disadvantage on perception and investigation checks for 1 minute. Affected creatures can attempt additional saves at the end of each of their turns, ending the effect on a success.</p>\n</div>\n</div>\n</div>",
